Returns the source file that this key will store a value to in the Persistence Network. For instance, in your persistence.ini file, if you have the entry "storage.test.**=json:///path/to/file.json", then reflect_value_source('storage.test.testing') would return 'json:///path/to/file.json'. This is useful for debugging, as it will definitively trace back the source/destination of a value.
